  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But looking back on it, they were quite-- it wasn't so easy to be-- it-- it really wasn't-- it was very good of them to really share their food with me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were not paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no contact with anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I [? would ?] because I have for so long, you know, remember the bad things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly I think, well, would I have done it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It was very risky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and quite apart from everything, they had so little food for their own children, that they shared what they had with me and I was a complete stranger.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew nothing about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was frightened of them because at some point I realized that they guessed that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was trying to sort of say that my father was some important person in the underground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that, you know, they would probably get money after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never told them I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I sort of realized at some point when they shouted at me, that they-- they guessed that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
